speeches.content:
**Have you ever desired that Members of Parliament would converse in straightforward English?** 

 &nbsp; 

 We render the formal discourse of Parliament into everyday language, allowing you to stay informed about all proceedings.

 &nbsp; 

 Peruse the discussions in the sidebar to access analysis and informal summaries of every debate occurring in the House of Commons, House of Lords, and beyond.

